{"type":null,"faqId":10512,"title":"P6-U06   音乐","answer":"<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t1.<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">艺术家、专辑、歌曲、播放列表的含义介绍</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">专</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">辑：按照专辑名分类的，属同一专辑的歌曲放在一个目录下。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">艺</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">术</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家：按演唱者分类的，属同一个演唱者的歌曲放在一个目录下。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">歌</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">曲：按照命名规则排序存放在一个大目录下。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">风</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">格：按照风格类型分类的，属同一种风格的歌曲放在一个目录下。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放列表：可以自定义列表添加喜欢的音乐文件。</span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">建立音乐播放列表</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在音乐</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用中打开我的歌单，并点击新建歌单。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在弹出的界面上输入歌单的名称，输入后点击保存。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">接着会弹出一个提醒框，提醒添加歌曲到歌单中，点击<b>确定</b>。然后选择自己想要添加的歌曲，选择完后，点击完成。</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31691\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31693\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">播放模式介绍</span> \n</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">顺序播放（默认）：播放列表中歌曲从第一首到最后一首，顺序播放，播完停止。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">随机播放：播放列表中的歌曲被无序播放，每首都播过一次后，播放停止。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全曲循环播放：播放列表中的歌曲从头到尾按顺序播放，播完一遍后会再重新播放。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">单曲循环播放：当前播放的歌曲被反复播放。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">随机播放</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全曲循环播放：播放列表中的歌曲被无序播放，播完后仍重复播放。</span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">后台播放与退出音乐，歌词同步</span> \n</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后台播放：进入音乐</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放器</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放任意音频文件</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">播放过程中按</span><span>back</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">或</span><span>home</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:63.8pt;text-indent:-13.9pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">退出音乐：在音乐播放界面，点击手机</span><span>Menu</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键，选择退出，在弹出的框上选择确定，即可退出音乐</span><span>+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;text-indent:-18.53333282470703px;white-space:normal;\">l</span><span style=\"font-size:7pt;text-indent:-18.53333282470703px;white-space:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;</span>歌词同步：当歌曲和对应的歌词存储在手机同一目录时，用户播放这首歌曲，歌词会自动加载。在播放界面，</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;点击播放进度条上方的小三角按钮，可以打开歌词界面。在歌词界面，点击歌词，在界面会有两个按钮“延迟</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">秒”、“快进</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">秒”，分别会将歌词延迟</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">秒和快进</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">秒。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1200","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null